io.orchestrate.client

Class DistanceAggregateResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.orchestrate.client.AggregateResult
      • io.orchestrate.client.DistanceAggregateResult

  • public class DistanceAggregateResult
extends AggregateResult
    This class represents the results of a DistanceAggregate function. The list of RangeBucket objects included with this aggregate indicate how many geo-point objects in the designated database field were found within each distance interval from the central anchor point.

    • Method Summary

      java.util.List<RangeBucket> getBuckets()

    • Method Detail

      • getBuckets

        public java.util.List<RangeBucket> getBuckets()
        Returns a list of RangeBuckets representing the number of geo-point field values found within each distance interval from the central anchor point designated in the accompanying distance query (inside the mandatory NEAR clause). Likewise, the bounds of the range are expressed in terms of the same distance units (miles, kilometers, etc) used within the accompanying distance query.
        Returns:
        The range buckets.
